<span class="text_title">About us</span>
<br /><br />
GamersEvents provides gaming event organisers a way to list their event free of charge, ensuring their event is known to a wide range of gamers in their area. GamersEvents allows gamers to find events in their area, ensuring they never have to miss something good because they didn't know it was on.
<br /><br />
Launched on 16 November 2007 at the eGames Expo, the site was conceived and created by Guy (Yug) Blomberg and Matt Burgess, the team behind the popular gaming comic/news/reviews website <a href="http://www.australiangamer.com">AustralianGamer.com</a>.